uary  reynoldsburg oh  the columbus dispatch obituaries powered bysearch services cotner funeral home  east main street reynoldsburg oh   website view map send flowers resources more obituaries for gary west looking for an obituary for a different person with this name gary l west obituary condolences west gary l west  of columbus passed away saturday november   he was a us army veteran and graduate of ohio university gary was a member of the ohio university alumni association retired from the social security administration and was scorekeeper for reynoldsburg girls basketball for many years he was preceded in death by his parents norman and kathryn west and brother norman kenneth west jr gary is survived by his sons anthony and eric west nephews karey and kris west niece kori west mccollum former wife and forever friend vicky mitchell many dear friends and members of the reynoldsburg athletic association family will receive friends  pm wednesday at cotner funeral home  e main st reynoldsburg where the funeral will be held at  am thursday burial will follow at glen rest memorial estate in lieu of flowers contributions may be made to the reynoldsburg athletic department messages may be sent to his family by visiting wwwcotnerfuneralhomecom published in the columbus dispatch on nov   read more remember share memories or express condolences below  entries the guest book is expired please restore the guest book to share in the life story for gary l west i worked with gary while we were both at social security while we were not close our paths crossedchristine vess restore the guest book resources send funeral flowers view funeral home details find advice  support funeral etiquette how to write a sympathy note  back to todays obituaries notify friends and family add the email addresses of friends or family members youd like to notify about this obituary to invalid to email from invalid from email message optional please provide me with special offers and discounts from l